{"tid":1569922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實唱《榮光》有咩問題？","createTime":"2019-09-14T20:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T20:35:43.000Z","uid":203508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8368ef175f0a54d09f79b3a9428fc562868500fe","tid":1569922,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:02:13.000Z","msg":"作為香港人，眼見抗爭運動元氣即將消耗殆盡<br />\n最令人擔心的解散先兆而經全部發生<br />\n勇武義士被殺被強姦被滅聲後仲俾香港人遺忘<br />\n快樂抗爭，無意義送頭/轉場，瘋狂唱歌打飛機<br />\n一開始團火變左唔理性既亢奮<br />\n街坊撚狗唱歌啊Q式洩憤換嚟既係大量傷亡<br />\n連想睇下連登都淨係得五毛分化post...<br />\n<br />\n其實八九六四俾左我地一個血的教訓<br />\n數以萬計既學生自殺式人鏈唱歌死守天安門<br />\n被解放軍用槍掃射仍然堅持前進<br />\n坦克車嚟到<br />\n學生唔係還擊 而係一齊瞓喺地下 最後俾坦克車碾成肉醬<br />\n<br />\n換嚟既 <br />\n係強國經濟爆炸式增長成為世界第二<br />\n支聯會民主黨繼續係香港唱歌<br />\n係班學生話俾共産黨聽<br />\n做壞事係無後果架 甚至乎會發達添！<br />\n<br />\n(轉貼) 左膠思想起底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URHzY2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURHzY2b.png&h=1fb7b265&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bO8SLHe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbO8SLHe.png&h=55d3a0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUFUAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUFUAB.png&h=62dd45c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gtJzeAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgtJzeAC.png&h=2492c7a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ma0hWOY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fma0hWOY.png&h=2ed5b81c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwV9NVE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqwV9NVE.png&h=f8e3dd3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQy3Snk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQy3Snk.png&h=e43df19c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCG83t1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn